OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAfter a cool start, it will
OL,6,Fbe a dry day, with variable amounts of
OL,7,Fcloud and some bright or sunny spells.
OL,8,FFeeling cooler compared to previous
OL,9,Fdays. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FUnsettled
OL,12,Fwith an increasing likelihood of wet
OL,13,Fand windy conditions on Friday and
OL,14,Finto the weekend. Drier, brighter and
OL,15,Fwindy on Sunday. Feeling cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
